<p>Spaced – en and — em dashes appear mid-line.</p>
<p>A word hugging three word-– folds to a hyphen and en dash.</p>
<p>A word hugging four word-— folds to a hyphen and em dash.</p>
<p>Two hyphens word-- stay literal before a space.</p>
<p>A trailing run sits at the very end --</p>
